     \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"96efba42\",\n            \"seq\": 101\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776162161200,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 147334,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776162044660,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776162158012,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 113352,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"I see the issue now. The latest commit on `feature/clean-architecture-migration` is from **2026-03-30** (March 30). We're now on **2026-04-14** — that's **15 days ago**! The branch hasn't been updated with our bug fixes. \\n\\nSo the pipeline status:\\n- Latest commit on branch: `47d53ae1` from March 30, 2026 (15 days ago)\\n- Latest pipeline: success from March 30, 2026\\n- MR !166 is mergeable (`merge_status: \\\"can_be_merged\\\"`) — it passed CI on March 30\\n\\n\\n- Now I need to verify whether our recent bug fixes are actually committed to this branch, since the workspace shows `git status` indicating changes were made to the codebase.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_kwoyvitaw7k7_1\",\n              \"name\": \"exec\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"command\": \"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-backend/.git 2>/dev/null && echo \\\"GIT EXISTS\\\" || echo \\\"NO GIT\\\"\",\n                \"timeout\": 3\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 1623,\n            \"output\": 248,\n            \"totalTokens\": 147316,\n            \"cacheRead\": 143243,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 2202,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776162133416,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d485700d5aaf3505d786874388a65\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"5534f29c\",\n            \"seq\": 1255\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"The workspace has no git! That means the bug fixes we made to the DTLX backend code are NOT in any git repo. The fixes are only in the local dist/ folder. This is a problem.\\n\\nNow let me report back to Lead about the GitLab CI situation:\\n\\n1. **Pipeline is not slow** — there are NO running pipelines at all\\n2. **Last pipeline**: 2026-03-30 (15 days ago), MR !166 — passed successfully  \\n3. **Pipeline speed**: ~3 minutes (not slow when it runs)\\n4. **Current MR !166**: mergeable, no new pipelines needed\\n\\n\\n5. **The real issue**: Our local bug fixes aren't committed to the feature branch since there's no git repo here, so the CI pipeline reflects the codebase from two weeks ago. The shared runners might be unavailable or have changed their status.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"---\\n\\n## 🌐 GitLab CI Check — DTLX Backend\\n\\n### Tình trạng pipeline\\n\\n| Item | Status |\\n|---|---|\\n| Pipeline running | **NONE** (không có pipeline nào đang chạy) |\\n| Pipeline cuối | **2026-03-30** (15 ngày trước) — MR !166 ✅ success |\\n| Thời gian chạy | **~3 phút** — không chậm |\\n| MR !166 | **Mergeable** — có thể merge ngay |\\n\\n### Không phải attack — vấn đề thực sự:\\n\\n**GitLab không nhận được code mới từ 15 ngày qua.**\\n\\nCommits mới nhất trên `feature/clean-architecture-migration`:\\n```\\n47d53ae1 — 2026-03-30 09:14 (15 ngày trước) — \\\"chore: course student repository\\\"\\n4a570ad6 — 2026-03-30 09:12 — \\\"chore: remove folder openspec\\\"\\n27f375b8 — 2026-03-30 09:08 — \\\"chore: implement prettier\\\"\\n```\\n\\n**Các bug fix hôm nay chưa được push lên git** — workspace DTLX BE hiện tại **không có git**. Code chạy local trong `dist/` nhưng không có repo git để push lên GitLab.\\n\\n### Hướng xử lý\\n\\nMuốn đẩy các bug fix (4 bugs đã fix) lên GitLab để trigger pipeline không?\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 123,\n            \"output\": 549,\n            \"totalTokens\": 147883,\n            \"cacheRead\": 145105,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 2106,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776162143517,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d486107384787d72be69212a976dc\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"02d899f5\",\n            \"seq\": 1257\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":6,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776165253486,"sessionId":"59cbabce-7c09-4f33-99e9-9cb3dea5f443","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":41124,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776165253037,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/59cbabce-7c09-4f33-99e9-9cb3dea5f443.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31 5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nC